'''阿克夏·卡納'''是印度的演員。1975年生于[[孟買|孟買]]，他曾演過很多成功的印度電影，並兩度得到[[印度電影觀眾獎|印度電影觀眾獎]]。

== 個人生活 ==
阿克夏的父親是演員[[維諾德·卡納|維諾德·卡納]]（[[Vinod_Khanna|Vinod Khanna]]），兄弟是演員[[拉胡·卡納|拉胡·卡納]]（[[Rahul_Khanna|Rahul Khanna]]）。阿克夏現今未婚，曾與演員[[塔拉·夏馬|塔拉·夏馬]]（Tara Sharma）約會。

== 電影事業 ==
1997年，22歲的阿克夏作為新人出在由其父親導演的影片《''喜馬拉雅山莊''》（''Himalaya Putra''）中，影片卻不是很成功。次年再出於[[J._P._Dutta|J. P. Dutta]]導演的影片《[[茫茫國界|茫茫國界]]》（''[[Border_(film)|Border]]''），影片獲得好評，他開始出名，後來兩次獲得[[印度電影觀眾獎|印度電影觀眾獎]]，並逐漸為印度觀眾所接受。<!-- (1997). The film did very well at the box office, becoming the highest grossing film of that year<ref>[http://www.boxofficeindia.com/1997.htm]</ref> and earning him a [[Filmfare_Best_Debut_Award|Filmfare Best Debut Award]]. Most of his releases that followed failed to do well until [[Subhash_Ghai|Subhash Ghai]]'s ''[[Taal_(film)|Taal]]'' (1999) released. The film fared moderately well and became the fourth highest grossing film of 1999 --><ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20040402124634/http://www.boxofficeindia.com/1999.htm]</ref><!-- This was followed by [[Farhan_Akhtar|Farhan Akhtar]]'s moderately successful ''[[Dil_Chahta_Hai|Dil Chahta Hai]]'' (2001) which became the fifth highest grossing film of 2001 --><ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20060212104051/http://www.boxofficeindia.com/2001.htm]</ref> <!-- His performance was well received by critics --><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.indiafm.com/movies/review/6738/index.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2007-11-13 |archive-date=2007-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071103092151/http://www.indiafm.com/movies/review/6738/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 

